sentences.english: The commanding general in the case says he will not seek the death penalty.
sentences.chinese: 這個事件中的主將說，他就不會要求死刑。

sentences.english: SHAKIR:And that Allah might help you with a mighty help.
sentences.chinese: 真主將給你一種有力的援助。

sentences.english: Like I told you all,kissing a princess breaks the spell.
sentences.chinese: 就像我說的那樣，吻一位公主將打破魔咒。

sentences.english: The chief architect of post war Republican organizational strength into Ohio was Ray C. Bliss .
sentences.chinese: 戰後組織俄亥俄州共和黨力量的主將是雷兒布利斯。

sentences.english: Many families and small business owners will have health insurance for the very first time in their lives.
sentences.chinese: 許多家庭和小企業主將會極早的獲得醫療保險。

sentences.english: As a subordinate general, you have to cooperate fully with the commanding general.
sentences.chinese: 身爲裨將，必須努力配合主將的工作。

sentences.english: And he set them in the firmament of heaven to shine upon the earth.
sentences.chinese: 天主將星宿擺列在天空，照耀大地。

sentences.english: Geraldine - Lords will take and hold strongholds in the first version of DnL.
sentences.chinese: 在黑暗與光明的第一版本中，領主將擁有並控制據點。

sentences.english: And the Lord delivered Jehoiakim king of Judah into his hand, along with some of the articles from the temple of God.
sentences.chinese: 主將猶大王約雅敬，並神殿中器皿的幾分交付他手。

sentences.english: That prince may lose her aureole whenever he find a ugly moment on her.
sentences.chinese: 一旦你看到她醜陋的一刻，公主將會失去光環。

sentences.english: The storekeeper will have closed his store by 6 o'clock this evening.
sentences.chinese: 今天傍晚六點鐘，那位店主將已關店了。

sentences.english: And so the Lord scattered them from that place into all lands, and they ceased to build the city.
sentences.chinese: 於是上主將他們分散到全地面，他們遂停止建造那城。

sentences.english: Although he is the representative of the rural literature, his works focus on city.
sentences.chinese: 作爲鄉土文學的主將，他卻進行着都市題材的創作。

sentences.english: Seller will withdraw offer unless accept by tomorrow noon.
sentences.chinese: 除非明日午前接受，否則賣主將撤消報價。

sentences.english: Some local Internet cafe owners have been asked to shut down for nearly a month, the report said.
sentences.chinese: 報道中提到，一些當地網吧業主將暫停營業近1個月。

sentences.english: Philip saith unto him, Lord, shew us the Father, and it sufficeth us.
sentences.chinese: 腓力對他說，求主將父顯給我們看，我們就知足了。
